                    these projects can be completed during art lessons, or even
                    used for parties - the possibilities are ENDLESS!
                </p>

                <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto space-y-4">
                    <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
                        <div
                            class="bg-white rounded-full p-1 mt-1 shrink-0"
                        >
                            <svg
